{"tha-ap364:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap364:0.2":"Mandaravapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap364:0.3":"Kakkarupupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap364:1.1":"“Yama deva idhagantva, ","tha-ap364:1.2":"gotamam sirivacchasam; ","tha-ap364:1.3":"Kakkarumalam paggayha, ","tha-ap364:1.4":"buddhassa abhiropayim. ","tha-ap364:2.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap364:2.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap364:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap364:2.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap364:3.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap364:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap364:3.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap364:4.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kakkarupupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap364:5.1":"Kakkarupupphiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}